Sponsored Topics








































See a problem?
Let us know!


  
  
            Located in Duarte, Calif., RBC Southwest Products Inc./US Bearing is a part of the RBC Bearings Incorporated and one of the leading international manufacturers and marketers of engineered precision bearings and components. Founded in 1919, the company produces highly technical and regulated bearing products. It has a staff of engineers that specialize in sophisticated design, testing and manufacturing. RBC Bearings Incorporated serves diversified industrial, aerospace and defense markets. Headquartered in Oxford, Conn., the company has more than 1,800 employees. RBC Bearings Incorporated operates more than 15 manufacturing facilities in several countries. Its aerospace divisions are well with many bearing materials, including standard 52100, 440C and 15-5/17-4 stainless products.
          






















